java.awt.LayoutManager, javax.swing.SwingConstants
public final class ExtWindowsScrollBarUI
extends com.sun.java.swing.plaf.windows.WindowsScrollBarUI

The JGoodies Windows Look and Feel implementation of ScrollBarUI.

It differs from Sun's Windows Look in that it paints black button triangles and that it honors the ScrollBar.width property to determine the preferred size. In 1.3 environments, this property is set honoring the screen resolution.

Author:
Karsten Lentzsch
